{"tid":689711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「全裸男僕女僕」紅爆澳洲 時薪可達近千元","createTime":"2018-06-04T09:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T09:41:24.000Z","uid":75969,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"addea211fd17495d38624bced7ba53f22619b66d","tid":689711,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180604/_2018060416520283091.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180604%2F_2018060416520283091.jpg&h=647632fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲近來興起一項新的熱門工作，以鐘點計時的「裸體清潔工」，這些「男僕」、「女僕」會按照客戶的喜好來搭配服裝進行打掃，若需要全裸也沒問題。更令人震驚的是，他們的收入每小時最高可達160澳幣 (約958港元)，甚至超過了澳洲時薪最高的技術工人。<br />\n<br />\n提供這個服務的是一家名為「遊戲時光娛樂」(Playtime Entertainment) 的公司，由27歲的布里斯班男子Shane Kemp創辦而成。Kemp之前是一名脫衣舞男，他在3年前舉辦一場派對後，忽發奇想地請了一名成人行業的女子來打掃家居，繼而獲得靈感創辦了這間公司。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，Kemp公司旗下目前有約95名女性和20多名男性員工，客戶可以自行要求清潔人員的裝扮，從露胸的女僕裝、只穿丁字褲，到全裸上陣都可以滿足，而每小時的收費則從80澳幣到160澳幣 (約480至958港元) 不等。要知道，這份工作的薪酬收入遠遠超過了澳洲工資最高的技術工人，最高時薪甚至是一倍有多。<br />\n<br />\n不過，這項特殊的服務在澳洲打開市場後，網友們的抨擊聲也逐漸加強，稱其「性別歧視有辱人格」，但Kemp對此回應「我們既有男性僱員，也有女性僱員，所以我認為並不存在性別歧視。而且我們很多客戶都是很孤單的人，只是希望有人陪伴，打掃完可以和他 (她) 們聊天。」<br />\n<br />\n「說實話，這份工作讓人上癮，因為賺錢太容易了。」Kemp續道，「而且在工作工程中有規定『禁止觸碰』，再加上我自己當過脫衣舞者，所以知道要採取哪些措施保障僱員的人身安全。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180604/_2018060416520363844.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180604%2F_2018060416520363844.jpg&h=faa991a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">創辦人Shane Kemp。網圖<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/732448\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F732448&d=tHsmTRW3e9CiP7rKxo%2B%2F1MmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=6afd1f94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F732448&h=a66b5b8b\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/732448</a>"},{"pid":"e28fcac81f6194457226a1a70bd3377ffd8bfab9","tid":689711,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:33:04.000Z","msg":"全裸？"},{"pid":"7c9293c4ad33202457694cd9cf7caf7ca72aeb0b","tid":689711,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:33:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b9a75a7e0d256a2d07eea13b7f63d9a4899e45","tid":689711,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"可唔可以射落地叫佢掃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2184053cb796c67c047516ee4895caf8b5a09433","tid":689711,"uid":157362,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:39:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c080211a7be6e0a535b970247bb10721ffb80147","tid":689711,"uid":12468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:39:53.000Z","msg":"條仔好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b677692d3bfe5488251d68e637600ede4efc2f0","tid":689711,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:39:55.000Z","msg":"呢間?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://playtentertainment.com.au/girls/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplaytentertainment.com.au%2Fgirls%2F&d=tHsmTRW3e9CiP7rKxo%2B%2F1MmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=9fabcfbf\" target=\"_blank\">http://playtentertainment.com.au/girls/</a>"},{"pid":"5e1d84134d965d26ec4fa34ab042a050ec8ce389","tid":689711,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2184053cb796c67c047516ee4895caf8b5a09433","tid":689711,"uid":157362,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:39:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2